scripts.comment: “外观”组简介 - 添加背景 Intro to "Looks" group - add background
点击右下角的“舞台”即可对“舞台”进行更改 要返回此处，请单击右侧的“Sprite” click on "Stage" on the bottom right to go to make changes to "Stage" to return to here, click on "Sprite" on the right
进入“舞台”中的“服装”导入背景图片 图片可以是外部照片 go to "Costumes" within "Stage" to import backgroun images images can be external photos
从“背景”导入背景图片 文件 -> 背景 从外部照片导入背景图片 文件 -> 导入 to import background images from "backgrounds" Files -> Backgrounds to import background images from external photos Files -> Import
